<HEAD>

<TITLE>VIA Kit Online: Tools: Creating a Local Visitor Industry Awareness Campaign</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<a href="../index.htm"><img align=bottom src="../gifs/tico.gif" border=0 alt="Oregon Welcomes You!"></a>

<a href="../via.htm"><img align=bottom src="../gifs/visitor.gif" border=0 alt="Visitor Industry Awareness Campaign"></a>

<a href="viakit.htm"><img align=bottom src="../gifs/kit.gif" border=0 alt="Visitor Industry Awareness Campaign"></a>
<p>
<a href="overview.htm">Overview</a> - 
<a href="resear.htm">Research</a> - 
<a href="resource.htm">Resources</a> - 
<a href="govt.htm">Government</a> - 
<a href="medi.htm">Media Relations</a> - 
<a href="tools.htm">Tools And Ideas</a>

<br><HR>
<H1>Creating a Local Visitor Industry Awareness Campaign</H1>

<H2>Form a Task Force or Committee</H2>

<OL>
<LI>Assemble a list of key individuals from all types of businesses
and agencies who have a stake in the success of local tourism
efforts.
<LI>Create a clearly defined list of issues and/or problem statements.
<LI>Brainstorm ideas and solutions for resolving the above.
</OL>

<P>

<H2>Create a Campaign Plan</H2>

<OL>
<LI>Create a campaign purpose or mission statement.
<LI>Designate a maximum of five goals that will accomplish the
purpose.
<LI>Choose campaign target groups or audiences that accomplish
the goals.
<LI>Establish timelines.
<LI>Assign individuals or teams to accomplish goals.
</OL>

<P>

<H2>Choosing Activities and Tools</H2>

<OL>
<LI>Review the VIA kit ideas and materials to choose those that
fit your plan.
<LI>Order materials and consult with the coordinator if needed.
</OL>

<P>

<H2>Implementation</H2>

<OL>
<LI>Create a calendar that coincides with timelines and targets
and match it to the type of materials and tools to be used (i.e.
press releases, stickers, events).
<LI>Assign specific teams and tasks for each element of the campaign
(i.e. publicity, business contact, special events).
</OL>

<P>

<H2>Evaluation</H2>

<OL>
<LI>Refer back to the original problem or issue statement. How
did you do in accomplishing your goal?
<LI>Conduct informal surveys, assess revenues and business activity.
<LI>Evaluate the possibility and feasibility of ongoing and/or
future campaigns.
</OL>

<P>

<P>
Source: J. Porter and Associates (October 1995)
<P>
File name: LOCAL.DOC
<P>
Download this file at: <A HREF="ftp://ftp.tico.org/viakit">ftp://ftp.tico.org/viakit</A>
</BODY>

</HTML>

</DOC>
