<HEAD>

<TITLE>Web Page Services through TICO’s Web Site: Oregon Welcomes You!
</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<a name="top" href="index.htm"><img align=bottom src="gifs/tico.gif" border=0 alt="Oregon Welcomes You!"></a>

<a href="member.htm"><img align=bottom src="gifs/member.gif" height=50 border=0 alt="back"></a>
<p>

<h1>Web Page Services through TICO’s Web Site: <i>Oregon Welcomes You!</i></h1>
<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#create">Creating your own Web Page on <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b></a>
<li><a href="#link">Creating a Link from <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> to your own Home Page</a>
<li><a href="#link">Other Page Services offered through <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b></a>
<li><a href="#submit">Submission Requirements for all Web Page material</a>
<li><a href="#order">Ordering/Information</a>
</ul>
<p>
<HR>
<P>

<a name="create"><H2>Creating your own Web Page
Through TICO's Web Site: <I>Oregon Welcomes You!</I></H2></a>

<P>
TICO provides discounted Web page design and storage services
for anyone belonging to a TICO member organization.  Non-members
may also develop web pages through TICO at a slightly higher rate.
<P>
All web pages include:
<UL>
<LI>A web page address for your organization that stays the same
even if you change or expand your web page.
<LI>Daily and monthly statistics on how often your page is being
visited
<LI>A link to the <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> home page
<LI>A listing in the statewide searchable database: <i>The Oregon
Directory</i>
</UL>

<P>
<HR>

<P>
<H1>Types of Web Pages Available Through TICO</H1>
<P>
<a href="#1">&quot;The Business Card&quot;</a>  -  <a href="#2">&quot;The Yellow Page Ad&quot;</a>  -  <a href="#3">&quot;The Brochure&quot;</a>  -  <a href="#4">&quot;The Travel Guide&quot;</a>
<P>

<HR>
<a name="1"><H2>1. &quot;The Business Card&quot;</H2></a>
Features:
<UL>
<LI>The name, address and phone number of your organizaiton
<LI>A contact e-mail address that users can click on and send
you e-mail right from your web page.
<LI>One logo, photo, or graphic
</UL>

Cost: 
<UL>
<LI>Design:  $75
<LI>Storage:  $25/year
</UL>

<P>

<a href="#order">Place an Order</a><BR>
<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>

<P>

<HR>
<a name="2"><H2>2. &quot;The Yellow Page Ad&quot;</H2></a>

Features:
<UL>
<LI>All the features of &quot;The Business Card&quot;, plus...
<LI>Up to 500 words of text describing your organization, event,
or service.
<LI>An additional logo, photo, or graphic
</UL>

Cost:
<UL>
<LI>Design:  $125
<LI>Storage:  $35/year
</UL>

<P>

<a href="#order">Place an Order</a><BR>
<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>

<P>


<HR>
<a name="3"><H2>3. &quot;The Brochure&quot;</H2></a>

Features:
<UL>
<LI>All the features of &quot;The Business Card&quot; and &quot;The
Yellow Page Ad&quot;, plus...
<LI>Up to 2500 words of text describing your organization, event,
or service.
<LI>Three additional images
</UL>

Cost:
<UL>
<LI>Design:  $185
<LI>Storage:  $60/year
</UL>

<P>

<a href="#order">Place an Order</a><BR>
<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>

<P>


<HR>
<a name="4"><H2>4. &quot;The Travel Guide&quot;</H2></a>

Features:
<UL>
<LI>A home page having all the features of &quot;The Business
Card&quot;, &quot;The Yellow Page Ad&quot; and &quot;The Brochure&quot;,
plus...
<LI>An additional four pages having all the features of &quot;The
Brochure&quot;
</UL>

Cost:
<UL>
<LI>Design:  $490
<LI>Storage:  $175/year
</UL>

<P>

<a href="#order">Place an Order</a><BR>
<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>

<P>

<HR>

<a name="link"><H2>Linking/Other Services</H2></a>

<P>
<B>1. Link from the <I>Oregon Directory</I> to a web page</B>
<UL>
<LI>Setup: $25
<LI>Yearly fee: $25
</UL>

<P>
<B>2. Link from the <I>Oregon Directory</I> to an e-mail address</B>
<UL>
<LI>Setup: $25
<LI>Yearly fee: $25
</UL>

<P>
<B>3. Listing in the <I>Oregon Directory</I></B>
<UL>
<LI>Setup: $25
<LI>Yearly fee: $25
</UL>

<P>
<B>Prices for other options or custom page design are available
upon request.</B>
<P>
<HR>
<B>Non-Member Pricing</B>
<P>
For organizations that do not belong to a TICO organization add
an additional 15% for design and storage.
<P>

<a href="#order">Place an Order</a><BR>
<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>
<P>

<HR>
<a name="submit><H2>Submission Requirements</H2></a>

<P>
<B>Images</B>
<P>
Copyright notice:  All images, including photos, graphics, and
logos, must be property of your organization in order to be included
on your web page.  Photographs that are not photos of your facility
must be accompanied by either a letter or release form by the
photographer.
<P>
Images will be scaled to approximately the following sizes:
<P>
Square and round images: 3x3 inches
<P>
Rectangular images:  3x5 inches or 5x3 inches depending on orientation
<P>
<B>Text</B>
<P>
Submit your text on a 3.5&quot; disk in either Windows, DOS, or
Macintosh format.  Text should be saved in plain text (ASCII)
format.  Include a hard copy of the text with suggested formatting
(i.e. size, alignment, bold, etc.)  Text may also be sent by e-mail
to <a href "mailto:webmaster@tico.org">webmaster@tico.org</a>.
<P>

<a href="#order">Place an Order</a><BR>
<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>
<P>
<HR>

<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="http://www.tico.org/cgi-bin/formmail.pl">
<input type=hidden name="recipient" value="sales@tico.org">
<input type=hidden name="subject" value="web page orders">
<input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="http://www.tico.org/index.htm">

<a name="order"><H2>Ordering Information</H2></a>

<P>
Thank you for your interest in being a part of TICO's <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> web site. So that we can better serve you and your organization, please fill out the following form and a TICO Representative will contact you soon.
<P>

<pre>
Name of Organization   <input name="realname" type="text" size="44">
Name of Contact   <input name="contact" type="text" size="48">
Address   <input name="address" type="text" size="48">
City   <input name="city" type="text" size="25">       State   <input name="state" type="text" size="2">   Zip   <input name="zip" type="text" size="5">
Phone   <input name="phone" type="text" size="20">
E-Mail Address   <input name="username" type="text" size="40">
Web Page Address   <input name="webpage" type="text" size="40">
Name of TICO Organization you belong to:
<input name="tico org" type="text" size="50">
</pre>
<P>
<HR>
Please select the following Web Page Service(s) you and your organization are interested in.
<P>

<b>Standard Services</b><BR>
<select name="page type">
          <option>&quot;The Business Card&quot;
          <option>&quot;The Yellow Page Ad&quot;
          <option>&quot;The Brochure&quot;
          <option>&quot;The Travel Guide&quot;
          <option>None
   </select>
<p>
<b>Linking/Other Services</b><BR>
<input name="OD Listing" type=checkbox>   Listing in the <i>Oregon Directory</i><BR>
<input name="OD Web Link" type=checkbox>   Link from the <i>Oregon Directory</i> to a web page<BR>
<input name="OD e-mail link" type=checkbox>   Link from the <i>Oregon Directory</i> to an e-mail address

<P>
Thank you.
<input type="submit" value="Process Order"> <input type="reset">
<P>

<a href="#top">Back to the Top</a>
<P>

<hr>
<B> For more information call (541) 926-5604. Or e-mail us at <a href "mailto:webmaster@tico.org">webmaster@tico.org</a>.

</FORM>

