<HTML>

<HEAD>
<title>TICO Member Services - Member Pages - Becoming an Oregon Welcomes You! Sponsor</title>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<a href="index.htm"><img align=bottom src="gifs/tico.gif" border=0 alt="Oregon Welcomes You!"></a>

<a href="member.htm"><img align=bottom src="gifs/member.gif" height=50 border=0 alt="back"></a>
<p>

<h2>Becoming an <strong>Oregon Welcomes You!</strong> Sponsor</h2>
If your organization has an idea for something that you think would be a great part of <strong>Oregon Welcomes You!</strong>, you can submit a proposal to the Travel Industry Council of Oregon.<p>

Proposals must contain the following:<p>

<ul>
<li>A brief explanation of the idea
<li>How it would be integrated with <strong>Oregon Welcomes You!</strong>
<li>How you would pay for the development of your idea
<li>How to contact you and your organization
</ul>

<pre>Send your proposal to:
Oregon Welcomes You! Proposals
attention: Janet Porter
PO Box 20057
Keizer OR 97307</pre>

Or e-mail your proposal to: <a href="mailto: JanPorter@aol.com">Janet Porter</a><p>

You will receive a response within two weeks of the postmark of any mailed proposal, or the date the e-mail was sent.<p>
 
</BODY>

</HTML>


















