<p>

Welcome to the TICO Discussion Groups<p>

These discussion groups are scheduled to begin in mid-November 1995.  If you would like to sponsor these discussion groups or moderate a discussion group of interest to you, <a href="mailto:webmaster@tico.org">send e-mail to the TICO Web Master</a>.<p>
Here you can join in on discussions of interest to Tourism Industry members in Oregon.  If you have a topic you would like to discuss, stop by the "Generally Speaking" section and put in your vote.<p>

These discussions are sponsored by: TBA<p>

The facilitators for each group are: TBA<p>

<ul>
<li>Tourism and the Internet 
<li>Funding for the 21st Century   
<li>Partnership     
<li>Marketing    
<li>Increasing Profits
<li>Generally Speaking
</ul>
   

