<DOCOLDNO>IA066-000398-B010-428</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mannatech-inc.com:80/IVR.HTM 207.158.92.200 19970112182143 text/html 4588
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 12-Jan-97 18:18:45 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-2013)
