<HTML>
<HEAD>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<TITLE>Mannatech’s Automated Customer Service Agent</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.03z">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=5>Mannatech's Automated Customer Service
Agent<BR>
</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<I><FONT SIZE=2>Hello.  Welcome to Mannatech's Automated Customer
Service Agent. <BR>
</FONT></I>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Mannatech has a new online telephone system that
allows associates to quickly access information about orders,
checks, QV and leadership and All Star status.  To access the
IVR (Interactive Voice Response) system, call <B>(972) 602-3035</B>
and have your Control Number ready in order to log into the system.
 After gaining access to the IVR, select from the following menu
items:<BR>
</FONT>
<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Press <B>1</B> to access information about orders.
 You will need the order number to access this information.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Press <B>2</B> to access information about your
last 4 checks.  The last 4 digits of your Tax ID number is required
to access this information.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Press <B>3</B> to obtain the current month's
qualifying volume.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Press <B>4</B> to obtain your leadership and
All Star status (based on last commission run).</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Press <B>5</B> to access order, QV or leadership
and All Star information on associates in your downline.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Press <B>9</B> to disconnect from the IVR system.</FONT>
</UL>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2></FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>When accessing information through the IVR, you should
be aware of the following:<BR>
</FONT>
<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Orders cannot be placed through the IVR system.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Automatic orders cannot be checked because the
system requests an order number when accessing check information.
 The associate will not know the order number of an automatic
order.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>You can verify a <I>phone</I> order is in the
system 5 minutes after the order is placed.  Shipping information
for the order will not be available for 24 hours or until the
order is shipped.   </FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>A faxed or mailed order will be in the system
24 to 48 hours after the order is <I>received</I> by Mannatech.
 You must contact customer service to obtain the order number
for mailed and faxed orders.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Orders paid for with a credit card are not shipped
until the credit card clears processing.  Wait 1 business day
after placing the order before attempting to access information
about a credit card order. The IVR system will let you know if
there was a problem processing your credit card order.</FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Orders are shipped 24-48 hours after receipt
of an order (next day orders arriving before noon on a business
day are shipped same day).  The shipping status of an order and
its qualifying volume are automatically given as part of the order
information.</FONT>
</UL>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2></FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>We would like to hear what you think about Mannatech's
Automated Customer Service Agent.  Please fill out the questionnaire
below, add any suggestions you may have concerning the IVR system
on a separate sheet and fax your response to:</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>     Attn: IVR system</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>     Fax: (972) 641-8776</FONT>
<P>
<U><B><FONT SIZE=2>Questionnaire</FONT></B></U><B><FONT SIZE=2>:</FONT></B>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>(Please rate on a scale of 1-5 where 1 is Poor and
5 is Excellent)</FONT>
<OL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>How would you rate the sound quality of the IVR
system overall?  <U>   </U></FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>How helpful was the information provided by the
system?   <U>   </U></FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>How easy was the system to use?     <U>   </U></FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>How would you rate the overall performance of
the system?  <U>   </U></FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>What are the chances you will use the IVR system
in the future?  <U>   </U></FONT>
<LI><FONT SIZE=2>Was the information you received from the system
accurate?  (Yes/No) <U>   </U></FONT>
</OL>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=2>Attach additional sheets for comments as
necessary.</FONT></CENTER>
</BODY>
</HTML>
