 uncanny eye for opportunity and the energy to capitalize on it.<BR>Ray immediately saw the marketing potential of Fioretti's product formulations and labored with Caster to formulate a compensation plan that would benefit the distributors as much financially as the products would their health. Together, they have created what network marketing professionals unanimously agree is the most flexible, lucrative, and comprehensive bonus structure ever to grace the MLM industry-a genuine masterpiece. Ray knew from personal experience that the ideal plan could generate sufficient supplemental revenue to meet the immediate financial needs of the new part-time distributor, or quickly replace the income of the career-minded individual, and ultimately provide opportunity for unlimited wealth for everyone. The true test of a network marketing compensation plan is how quickly, and how many people with varying levels of activity and talent prosper through it. Their formulation worked. Not only did Ray make over one million dollars in less than two years, but we have hundreds of part-timers who substantially supplement their monthly incomes, many others who are making mid-to-high-five-figure monthly incomes, and another group approaching Ray's achievements. In short, the proof of our compensation plan's genius is in the large numbers of others who are fast approaching that "million dollars earned" mark themselves.<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
