t people can appreciate the value of these products."<BR>Mark selected Mannatech for several reasons: "First, thorough research," he said. "Any type of supporting research I've ever requested, I've received. Every one of my questions has been answered. Mannatech has scientific evidence that people are seeing positive life-style changes through these products. Second, integrity," Mark continued. "The research team is a highly respected group. I've found that in no other MLM company. McAnalley, McDaniel and Fioretti are all accomplished scientists, but they don't hoard their knowledge. They use it to help all people understand why the products are so beneficial.<BR>"Most important," Mark emphasized, "the products work! When you take them on a continuous basis, you get positive results. In my line of work, that generates enthusiasm. When people feel better, they start making better choices about what they put in their bodies, and this helps them reach their goals faster. The fact that Mannatech products are natural makes them even more attractive to my clients. I believe Mannatech products are the best that have entered the fitness industry in years. I recommend them to everyone, because they really work."<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
