, they may be able to impact performance in a way that no other product could.<BR>Professional athletes are continually bombarded with opportunities to endorse a multitude of products with the promise that using the product will enhance their performance. So, it is very interesting that the athletes quoted on this page are not paid to endorse Mannatech's products. Through personal experience, they have recognized the value of these products, and they want to share them with as many people as possible. Their testimonials bear witness to the incredible potential of these products and their athletic achievements read like a who's who in athletic performance. Testimonials from some of the world's greatest athletes, coaches, and trainers as well as documented clinical tests results, have convinced me that Mannatech sport products are the best natural, nutritional non-toxic alternative to steroids and other dangerous performance enhancing drugs.<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><I>Reproduction of athlete and celebrity endorsements is strictly prohibited.</I></CENTER><H2>Professional Sports Coaches and Trainers</H2><IMG SRC="/pics/harg.jpg"><BR><BR><B>Mike Hargrove</B><BR>Manager, Cleveland Indians<BR><BR><BR><B>Rick Griffin</B><BR>Trainer, Seattle Mariners<BR><BR><BR><B>John D. Pease</B><BR>Assistant Coach, Jacksonville Jaguars<BR><BR><BR><B>Kent Johnston</B><BR>Strength and Conditioning Coach, Green Bay Packer<BR><BR><BR><B>Jerry W. Simmons</B><BR>Strength Coach, The Cleveland Browns<BR><BR><BR><B>Jerry Rhome</B><BR>Offensive Coordinator, Houston Oilers<BR><BR><BR><B>Bert Hill</B><BR>Strength/Conditioning Coach, Detroit Lions<BR><BR><BR><B>Tommy Nobis</B><BR>Player Personnel, Atlanta Falcons<BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><H2>Top Amateur Athletes, Coaches and Trainers</H2><B>Tom Tellez</B><BR>University of Houston Track Coach and Olympic Trainer<BR><BR><BR><IMG SRC="/pics/Law.jpg"><BR><BR><B>Debbi Lawrence</B