<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Mannatech Tomorrow Online</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><CENTER><A HREF="Tom.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/1aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Fin.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/2aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Ath.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/3aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Pro.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/4aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Act.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/5aBtn.jpg"></A><BR><A HREF="//www.mannatech-inc.com/"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/Hma.jpg"></A><BR><BR><A HREF="Tom.html">Tomorrow  |  </A><A HREF="Fin.html">Financial  |  </A><A HREF="Ath.html">Athletics  |  </A><A HREF="Pro.html">Products  |  </A><A HREF="Act.html">Action  |  </A><A HREF="//www.mannatech-inc.com/">Home</A><BR><BR><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><H1>Mannatech - The Cutting Edge in Nutraceutical Products</H1><I>by Sam Caster</I><BR><BR><BR></CENTER><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10 SRC="/pics/ManAmb.jpg">Dietary Supplements are predicted to become a multi-billion dollar industry. But what separates Mannatech products from the tens of thousands of other nutritional products? <BR>Mannatech is at the forefront of a widespread trend in research and development of carbohydrate-based products. However, rather than attempting to develop synthetic carbohydrates as drug companies are doing, Mannatech has developed naturally occurring, plant-derived, carbohydrate-based products. Rather than waiting until a person is sick to provide assistance, Mannatech's products are designed to use nutrients working through normal physiology to maintain optimal health through improved nutrition.<BR>Mannatech has filed a patent on the supplementation of eight specific monosaccharides used by the body in synthesis of glycoconjugates-cell-surface molecules that are important in cell-cell communication. Scientists are just beginning to identify the importance of this communication in supporting all functions of the body. <BR>Mannatech has been preparing for this unprecedented opportunity by scientifically testing and standardizing the functional components in other plants as well. The following segments will cover some of these beneficial plants used in the formulation of Mannatech's patent-protected products.<BR><BR><B>Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT></B><BR>The foundation of all Mannatech products is centered around the use of Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT> complex. Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT> describes Mannatech's new product line, which we believe contains the most important phytochemical discovery to date. This patent-protected complex is utilized as a stand-alone dietary support product, as a key ingredient in combination with other beneficial food components, and as the primary component in a unique line of skin care products. Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT> products are designed to help provide eight known monosaccharides used in glycoconjugate synthesis. Manapol&#174; powder helped provide one of these eight sugars.<BR>"Almost without exception whenever two or more living cells interact in a specific way, cell surface carbohydrates will be involved. From the first meeting of sperm and egg, through enbryogenesis, development and growth, carbohydrate molecules confer exquisite specificity upon cell-cell interactions. Complex carbohydrates are essential in the correct functioning of the body's immune defenses. . ." (Hodgson J. "Capitalizing on Carbohydrates". Biotechnology. 1991; 8:109).<BR><BR><B>The Precursors of Dioscorea</B><BR>There are more than 600 species of the botanical dioscorea. Certain species of the herb have been used anecdotally for centuries for relief of chronic conditions, as a fat-controlling agent, and as a lean tissue builder. Researchers believe the reason for these benefits is that these dioscorea species are storehouses of phytochemicals called plant sterols. Not found in our daily diets, these plant sterols may help support the body's natural production and balance of hormones. As hormones help regulate all metabolic processes, these functional food components could provide invaluable benefits in building and sustaining healthy bodies. Mannatech uses processing methods that provide a dioscorea complex with standardized levels of these plant sterols that, when combined with Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT> complex, could provide effective building blocks not obtainable in any other products.<BR><BR><B>Beyond Vitamins</B><BR>For years, companies have formulated vitamins, minerals and enzyme supplements for nutritional support. As controversy builds regarding the actual benefits of these supplements, scientists have found common ground in the exciting potential of phytochemicals. New processing techniques allow manufacturers to emulsify, dehydrate and freeze-dry raw fruits and vegetables. These techniques protect the essential components of the whole food, including the valuable phytochemicals, vitamins, minerals and enzymes, and provide them to the consumer in an effective and convenient manner.<BR>Mannatech is truly on the cutting edge in nutraceutical technology and is the clear frontrunner in the race to capture market share in this explosive new industry.<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
