buffed by Dr. Nugent, made a medical appointment to see him. "I was upset when I realized he wasn't a patient, that he came in to sell me something," Dr. Nugent says. "Little did I know that he had brought me products that I had been looking for my entire professional career. I gave him a hard time. As a research scientist, I wanted to deal in facts only."He returned, armed with information. I found that the company, the products and the leaders have exceptional credentials! Mannatech is not like the others, making claims without the evidence to support them.<BR>After a thorough analysis of the company, Dr. Nugent decided to try the Mannatech products. He now believes that among the things which set Mannatech apart are the company's dedication to research and to utilizing phytochemicals. "I teach my students to treat each patient as absolutely biochemically unique, because that is truly the case. It's pretty exciting to find all of the ideas and principles I've taught for years, concentrated in Mannatech. "It comes down to my philosophy: Never compromise. I think the health care potential in these products is beyond calculation."<BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
