ceutical. This is a blend of flash-dried: broccoli, brussel sprout, cabbage, carrot, cauliflower, garlic, kale, onion, papaya, pineapple, tomato, turnip and freeze-dried aloe vera."Matt  While Phil was reading above-"You shouldn't have read that while they're eating it."<BR><BR>Phil  (to the children) "What did you guys think?"<BR><BR>Lauren  "It's good."<BR><BR>Jonathan  "It's good."<BR>	"And it's healthy for you - what about that?"<BR><BR><BR>This is the same response all Mannatech Associates receive when they introduce Phyto&#183;Bears&#174;, but it's great to see it on National TV.<BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
