third-party business analysts. (see <A HREF="Nutra.html">Tomorrow Section, 4A</A>)<BR><BR><LI>Do patent-protected, proprietary, products exclusive to one company offer a better business opportunity than copycat products available everywhere at a variety of prices? (see <A HREF="Why.html">Financial Section, 3B</A>)<BR><BR><LI>Do the startup stages of a business offer greater business opportunities than the later stages? (see <A HREF="BsPros.html">Financial Section, 1B</A>)<BR><BR><LI>Do you see network marketing as a legitimate, effective marketing system? (see <A HREF="BsPros.html">Financial Section, 1B</A>)<BR><BR><LI>Is training an important element when you enter a new industry? Especially an industry projected to be six times larger than the current $4 billion nutritional market? (see <A HREF="Train.html">Action Section, 1E</A>)<BR><BR><LI>If you see Mannatech as having all the ingredients to be a major player in the emerging dietary supplement market, would you like to share in its financial success?<BR><BR>If you answered, "Yes!" to the above questions, you're ready to begin. Click <A HREF="Start.html">"Getting Started"</A>.</OL></td></tr></table><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
