<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Mannatech Tomorrow Online</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><CENTER><A HREF="Tom.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/1aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Fin.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/2aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Ath.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/3aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Pro.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/4aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Act.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/5aBtn.jpg"></A><BR><A HREF="//www.mannatech-inc.com/"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/pics/Hma.jpg"></A><BR><BR><A HREF="Tom.html">Tomorrow  |  </A><A HREF="Fin.html">Financial  |  </A><A HREF="Ath.html">Athletics  |  </A><A HREF="Pro.html">Products  |  </A><A HREF="Act.html">Action  |  </A><A HREF="//www.mannatech-inc.com/">Home</A><BR><BR><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><H1>Training Secures Opportunity</H1><I>by Richard Howard</I><BR><BR></CENTER><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10 SRC="/pics/How.jpg"><B>Facts Replace Hype. </B><BR>Fact: Mannatech is on the verge of becoming the leader in a new industry. This new industry called nutraceuticals is predicted to be the next financial blockbuster in this country. <BR>Fact: Mannatech owns the exclusive rights to Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT> complex, a major breakthrough in nutritional science and the first product with glyco-nutritional patent claims. <BR>So, this is not a game, not a hobby, nor a fleeting obsession for either the owners of Mannatech or for its growing number of business-minded Associates. Mannatech has at-tracted some of the world's best athletes, top health care professionals, and brightest marketing professionals for one reason - advanced technology. Once an individual experiences Mannatech products, they become a committed consumer. Once they learn about the technology behind the products, the future of nutraceuticals, and the financial opportunity associated with becoming a Mannatech Associate, they become committed business- builders. So, how does Mannatech plan to educate the multitudes? Through an aggressive two-stage training program. <BR>Stage one is called Master Associate Training. This training package includes Mannatech products (retail value exceeds the cost of the pack), a professional training and working manual, and live training on the company, products, marketing compensation, and an initial daily business plan for success. This training package is designed to teach the basic facts about the business and business-building skills as well as provide the materials needed to insure success for the part-time or full-time Associate. <BR>The next stage of training is the more comprehensive All-Star Training. This training package includes Mannatech products (retail value exceeds the cost of the package), professional training and working manual insert, and live training from company founders, researchers, doctors, and patent holders as well as top-producing Mannatech Associates. This training is designed to solidify the long-term potential of this opportunity through first-hand exposure to individuals who have discovered and patented the technology, formulated the products, developed the marketing strategies, and designed the operating systems. In addition, top producers are invited to train the advanced business-building techniques that have proven to get results.<BR>Mannatech has all the ingredients necessary to provide Associates with an unlimited financial opportunity. The company is well-financed, and owns the exclusive rights to Ambrotose<FONT SIZE=-3>(TM)</FONT> complex. The management team is seasoned, experienced, and has operated together for two years. The scientific team is unmatched in the development of carbohydrate-based nutraceuticals. Clinical data supports the effectiveness of the products. The only variable would be the level of commitment that each new Associate makes to this business. If you treat this business like a hobby, it will pay you likewise. If, however, you can truly grasp the significance of the opportunity that Mannatech provides, then make the commitment to be trained to succeed, it's a commitment that could change your life forever.<BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
