<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Mannatech Tomorrow Online</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><CENTER><A HREF="Tom.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="1aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Fin.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="2aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Ath.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="3aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Pro.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="4aBtn.jpg"></A><A HREF="Act.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="5aBtn.jpg"></A><BR><A HREF="//www.mannatech-inc.com/"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="Hma.jpg"></A><BR><BR><A HREF="Tom.html">Tomorrow  |  </A><A HREF="Fin.html">Financial  |  </A><A HREF="Ath.html">Athletics  |  </A><A HREF="Pro.html">Products  |  </A><A HREF="Act.html">Action  |  </A><A HREF="//www.mannatech-inc.com/">Home</A><BR><BR><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><H1>Which Income is Right For You?</H1><I>by David Colister</I><BR><BR><BR></CENTER>I asked our computer department at Mannatech to give us the hard facts about what the average incomes are for those coming in the various entry packs. We designed these packs for different objectives: the $49 pack for those whose real desire is to get our products at the least expensive price, the $229 pack for those who want to be educated consumers and receive a variety of products to try, and the $1,000 Career Pack for those who want to make as much money as possible as quickly as possible.<BR>We also understood that many people were purchasing the $49 and $229 packs with the intentions of building an organization and making a great income. We wanted to provide people with some hard data which clearly showed which pack was right for the business-minded Associate. Below are the average monthly incomes (September 1996) of active distributors.<BR><BR><BR><H2><A HREF="#Pack1">$49 Pack    /    $88 mo.</A></H2>Without Master Associate (MA) or All-Star (AS) training.<BR><BR><BR><BR><H2><A HREF="#Pack2">$229 Pack / $132 mo.</A></H2>With no All-Star training.<BR><BR><BR><BR><H2><A HREF="#Pack3">$1,000 Pack*  / $717 mo.</A></H2><B>Average of all All-Stars</B><BR><BR><BR><BR><H2><A HREF="#Pack3">$1,000 Pack*  / $1,508 mo.</A></H2><B>Regional Director (RD) or above</B><BR>	Regional Directors have sponsored four people and is only the first level of Leadership achievement (Presidential Director being the highest).<BR><BR><BR><BR><H2><A HREF="#Pack3">$1,000 Pack* / $8,209 mo.</A></H2><B>Four-Star RD or above</B><BR>	Regional Directors have sponsored four people and is only the first level of Leadership achievement (Presidential Director being the highest). Four-Stars are people who have sponsored four people who have had 12 people in their group enroll for MA or AS training. Mannatech has levels up to 16-Star Presidential.<BR><BR><BR><BR>Keep in mind that the above incomes are residual in nature (meaning that they keep coming in even if you are on a tropical island enjoying a family vacation) and reflect the incomes of people who have been building their businesses for no more than two years, nine months (age of Mannatech at the time of the data collection).<BR><BR> <I>*Includes those who have upgraded to Master Associate and All-Star training, and who have accumulated $600 personal wholesale volume.</I><BR<BR><BR><BR><table border=0><tr><td width=45><br></td><td width=380><CENTER><H2><A NAME="Pack3">$1,000 Career (All-Star Business) Pack</A></H2></CENTER><UL><LI>For business-minded Associates.<LI>Excellent sample inventory (28 units) of entire product line for establishing business growth momentum. Total retail value of products exceeds $1,000 which makes a career Associate's $1,000 investment into this pack 100% secured by inventory.<LI>Includes $600 Personal Wholesale Volume, covering first month's volume requirements.<LI>Opens up all Mannatech compensation plan revenue streams to the new Associate. Qualifies you to earn from: Master Associate (MA) and All-Star (AS) Corporate Training bonuses, all future Binary Income Centers, Leadership bonuses, etc. (the above mentioned being the most lucrative).<LI>Career training: 4+ hours of Master Associate training and 10+ hours of All-Star training.<LI>$100+ of sales and recruiting materials.<LI>Deluxe Mannatech organizer/planner with archiving system.</UL>Best dollar value for serious Mannatech Associate who wishes to be paid for all his or her activity.<BR><BR><BR><BR><CENTER><H2><A NAME="Pack2">$229 Master Associate Pack</A></H2></CENTER><UL><LI>For those seeking to be educated consumers.<LI>Seven products for personal use. Associate can become a "product of the products."<LI>Qualifies you to earn from: the Master Associate Corporate Training, the Binary (*only your #1 Income Center), and the Unilateral bonus plans.<LI>4+ hours of Master Associate training.<LI>Basic Mannatech organizer/planner.<LI>Additional tools and forms, including MA training manual.</UL><I>* Master Associate Packs do not include any Personal Wholesale Volume (PWV) and subsequently do  not qualify the new Associate for any sales volume accumulation of his/her downline Associates toward bonuses, including the above mentioned bonus plans as well as the All-Star Corporate Training bonuses, Leadership bonuses, and Binary Income Centers beyond the number one Income Center. To qualify for all of the Mannatech bonuses an Associate must have ordered (accumulatively) at least $600 in PWV, maintain MA and All-Star Trainer status, and order $90 PWV a month. These features (with the exception of the MA Trainer status) are NOT included in the $229 Associate Pack. </I><BR><BR><BR><BR><CENTER><H2><A NAME="Pack1">$49 Consumer Associate Pack</A></H2></CENTER><UL><LI>For those consumers seeking to purchase Mannatech products at wholesale prices.<LI>Qualifies new Associate for Unilateral and Binary (#1 Income Center only) bonuses.<LI>Small sampling of introductory literature.</UL>No PWV to qualify Associate for bonuses.<BR><BR>No free career training.<BR><BR>No Mannatech planner.<BR><BR>No participation in Corporate Training bonuses, Binary bonuses beyond the first Income Center (a new Income Center $1,200 is activated for every two personally sponsored Associates), or Leadership bonuses.<BR><BR><BR><BR>Which entry pack is right for you depends on your personal level of interest. For those business-minded people who want to maximize their income potential, the $1,000 Career Pack is the most economical and practical pack. For those who wish to be educated consumers and do not opt to earn all the bonuses stimulated by their business activities, the $229 Master Associate Pack is the most appropriate. And, finally, the $49 Consumer Associate Pack is perfect for those whose desire is to get the fine line of Mannatech products at the lowest possible prices.<BR><BR><BR></td></tr></table><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
