d multimedia application development.<BR>Our first CD will feature Mannatech's Optimal Health Plan. Hosting the video portions is Dr. John Branden (PhD, Clinical Nutrition) who has more than twenty years of clinical experience. Dr. Branden's work on individualized nutrition has received support from the highly regarded non-profit institution, the Price Pottenger Nutritional Foundation among others respected in the field ofhealth and nutrition.<BR>Among this CD's features are: <BR><UL><LI>An introduction to Mannatech's complete line of products.<LI>Videos, text, and graphics supporting the science behind these products.<LI>The Metabolic Profile survey and specific information related to the recommended diets.<LI>Information on fine tuning your diet and on exercise programs. 	<LI>Video interviews from Mannatech consumers, Scientific Teams and Management.<LI>An interactive lifestyle program to help the user track and achieve his/her weight loss, health, and fitness goals.<BR></UL><BR>This CD gives Mannatech Associates an incredible tool for developing product loyalty from our consumers.<BR>The second CD will be designed specifically as a recruiting tool. Polyphase will make certain that the Mannatech story is told in a compelling, interesting manner by showcasing Mannatech's unique qualities, our Associates, products, science and opportunity. Featured will be business-building testimonials, basic interface with Mannatech products and a section on compensation. As a recruiting tool, it stands alone. Your prospective Associate can browse through all the sections with ease or stop and take an in-depth look at any particular segment that interests him or her.<BR>Our two new CDs are only a taste of what the future has in store for Mannatech Associates. Very much like our proprietary health products, these clear, thorough, businesslike presentations will distinguish us from all competition.<BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
