ke advantage of all of the income potential available. This program provides all the necessary tools, training and product, you need to begin building a successful business.                         </UL><p>       </UL>        <UL>                  <LI><h4>Master Associate Pack (MA)</h4>                         <UL>                                  <LI>$229 of Mannatech products at retail cost.                                  <LI>Welcome Pack materials.                                  <LI>Master Associate training, materials, and qualification.                         </UL>        </UL><p><br><h3><LI>Complete the Associate Application.</h3><p><h3><LI>Complete the Discount Automatic Monthly Product Order Form.</h3><p><h3><LI>Start the 30-day Plan of Action providedin your materials.</h3><p><h3><LI>Start using the products.</h3><p><h3><LI>Learn to use the marketing tools.</h3><p><h3><LI>Attend the Master Associate Training as soon as possible.</h3><p><h3><LI>Attend the All-Star Training provided by the company as<br>soon as possible.</h3><p></OL><br></td></tr></table>The decision to take advantage of Mannatech's opportunity is one of the most valuable you will ever make. The long-term financial and health benefits are unequaled. <b>Don't delay, get started today.</b><p><br><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
