 business-building techniques and presentation materials. All-Stars are provided with a full year of daily planner materials and a training audio to help teach them how to incorporate a time management system into their daily routine. The Mannatech Day Planner creates a professional image for Associates and provides a proven system of organization to assist them in reaching their goals.<p><br><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
