und in the aloe leaf. Subsequently, over 66 patents have been issued worldwide to Carrington  Laboratories covering the isolation, characterization, stabilization, use and derivation process of this molecule. Dr. McAnalley was also instrumental in the development of Carrington  Laboratories nutritional-grade product Manapol&#174; powder. Subsequently licensed to Mannatech Inc.<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
