 using Mannatech products, I realized that I hadn't had an aspirin or used an ice pack in weeks! That's when I started thinking about friends who might benefit from these products.<BR>"It's one thing to see how much you benefit personally. To offer this kind of value to people you care about and then to create a business around it is something else. Since I started listening to Richard and doing what he said, it's been simple. Deborah and I became One-Stars almost without trying. Once you try these products, you're sold! My wife loves the products and the Mannatech opportunity. She's right! Once you use them, your life will never be the same."<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
