ey were always smiling. As I learned about the products and the company, I knew why! They have the vision to see, and the faith to endure. I share that.<BR>"You have to decide whether this is a hobby or a business for you. If it's a business, you need products and training. You can't sell from an empty wagon; you can't present information from an empty head! Know the products and the benefits. If it's unseen and untold, it's unsold!<BR>"Mannatech is unique. Nowhere else can such a small investment do so much to improve one's health and wealth. Mannatech," she says, "will help me bring my dreams to reality."<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
