y. <BR>When a friend phoned and asked them to look at Mannatech, they liked what they saw. Michelle called her father who had researched aloe to check this out. His report? "It's incredible." <BR>Cautious, Al took Em¥Pact and Sport and tested it on the volleyball team. Great results. "When Sam Caster came to Calgary, he answered every one of our questions," Michelle says. "Testimonials and physical results are more impressive than we first imagined. With Mannatech, we're now in a position to take care of our families. Mannatech makes it possible!"<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
