l products for 15 years, but we'd seen people get burned. Other companies just disappeared, so it was important to us to learn as much as we could. We spent three days at a Dallas meeting, visiting the home office, meeting the company officers, verifying the stability, soundness, integrity and longevity. We couldn't have been more im-pressed. We signed up!" <BR>Laughing, she rephrased a popular network marketing slogan: "The opportunity of a lifetime..." "Before you know whether it's the opportunity of a lifetime, you have to know how much lifetime there is in the opportunity! Mannatech's products are the key. In the future, we know Mannatech will be there!"<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
