mpleted a degree as a Naturopathic Doctor and a PhD in Nutrition. Alone with four young children and a mountain of debt, she found support and renewal in a 12-step program for families and friends of addicts. Mannatech was the gift that then appeared in her life.<BR>"Previous network marketing convinced me that the concept would work," Marcia says. "When I was introduced to Mannatech, I took the trouble to research it, to see whether it was as exceptional as it seems. My scrutiny revealed a serious company with sound business practices. It's here for the long run. Anyone with a serious interest in health or business must look at it."<BR><BR><BR><CENTER><HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=center SIZE=2><BR><FONT SIZE = 3>Available E-Mail addresses are as follows:<BR><A HREF="mailto:ldaniel@mail.mannatech-inc.com">Customer Service<BR> Email contact for customer service questions and problems.</A><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=-2>Copyright &copy; 1996 Mannatech, Inc. all rights reserved.<BR></FONT></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
