HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 12-Jan-97 20:18:58 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-2013)
Allow-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Monday, 16-Dec-96 18:26:56 GMT
