<B><FONT SIZE=-1> Welcome to Counsel Connect's Spotlight. Each week you'll find the full text of the hottest documents in the legal news -- from briefs and transcripts in the latest megabucks suit to leaked government reports and more. Don't ask us how we get some of these docs--we can't reveal our nonvirtual sources. But do check in regularly. Spotlight also features great news stories from our sister publications at American Lawyer Media. Enjoy. For more information on Counsel Connect's library, contact:</FONT></B><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>
