<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Counsel Connect Web - Internet Concierge</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=FFFFFF
VLINK=FF0000>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG WIDTH=442 HEIGHT=57 BORDER=0 SRC="/images/header.gif" ALT="COUNSEL CONNECT WEB"><BR CLEAR=ALL></P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG WIDTH=249 HEIGHT=29 SRC="/images/concierge.gif" ALT="THE INTERNET CONCIERGE"><BR CLEAR=ALL></P>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="0" CELLSPACING="5">
<TR>

<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=CENTER>
<! Generated by place_ad, W3.COM, 1996><! Ad placement failed for '2704' (no available graphics. *BDEad*. jj)><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>

<TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=CENTER>
<! Generated by place_ad, W3.COM, 1996><! Ad placement failed for '4704' (no available graphics. *KILLINGad*. jj)><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>

<TD ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=CENTER>
<! Generated by place_ad, W3.COM, 1996><! Ad placement failed for '5704' (no available graphics. *HEINTZad*. jj)><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<BLOCKQUOTE>

<P>The Internet may offer a wealth of information but mining out the nuggets you're looking for can be a frustrating experience. Of course, there are plenty of search engines out there -- but who has time to search each one and compile the results?</P>

<P>Enter the Internet Concierge: a living, breathing <I>human being </I> who will help you locate resources on the Internet. The Internet Concierge service is offered by Counsel Connect, the largest online community for lawyers. Our editors can teach you how to make the Internet an accessible legal research tool.</P>

<H3>What Is The Concierge?</H3>

<P>Let's say you're researching an environmental law issue, need information on breast implant litigation, or are curious about the anticipated impact of a bill pending in Congress. Ask the Internet Concierge to let you know what resources are available. The Concierge will conduct a comprehensive search using a variety of search engines. Search results, along with an explanation of how they were found, will be sent directly to your email box.</P>

<H3>What Can The Concierge Do?</H3>

<P>Here are some recent examples of how our service typically works:</P>

<UL>
<LI>Responding to a question about resources on labor and employment law in Ontario, Canada, the Concierge uncovered summaries of print guides by a number of legal publishers, a continuing legal education catalog, a guide to legislation published by the provincial government, and several newsletters published by law firms.<P>

<LI>A request for information on how the v-chip works yielded four websites and five newsgroups -- including FAQ files filled with v-chip information.<P>

<LI>A lawyer interested in suits brought against tobacco companies by state attorneys general was referred to the Court TV Law Library which contains electronic versions of key documents in these cases, along with a host of other relevant web sites.<P>

<LI>A lawyer who needed bankruptcy sources was provided with the searchable index of U.S. Supreme Court bankruptcty decisions, the American Bankruptcy Institute's homepage, the Internet Bankruptcy Library, and instructions on how to subscribe to two bankruptcy listservs.
</UL>

<H3>What Does The Concierge Service Cost?</H3>

<P>The service is free to Counsel Connect members. Non-members are charged $29.95 for each search.</P>

<H3>How Do I Start?</H3>

<P>Click on the 'Transmit' button below and enter your request. If your request is too broad, our editors will help refine your search. Replies are usually sent within 48 hours on business days.</P>

<FONT SIZE=+1> <P><B>I would like to <A HREF="inetconform.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="images/transmit.gif"></A> a request to the Internet Concierge. I understand that if I am not a CC member I will be charged $29.95 if the Internet Concierge conducts a successful search on my behalf, and that the Counsel Connect's billing department will call me to verify a major credit card number before forwarding my request to the Internet Concierge.</B></P></FONT>

</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
<A HREF="http://www.counsel.com/cgi-bin/htimage/images/toolbar.map"><IMG ISMAP WIDTH=503 HEIGHT=40 BORDER=0 SRC="/images/toolbar.gif" ALT=" "></A>
