<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Counsel Connect's QRFP</TITLE>
<LINK REV=MADE HREF="mailto:tdrucker@counsel.com">
<META HTTP-EQUIV="Reply-to" CONTENT="tdrucker@counsel.com (Todd Drucker)">
<META NAME="publication" CONTENT="Q.R.F.P. (Quick Request for Proposals)">
<META NAME="publisher" CONTENT="Counsel Connect">
<META NAME="keywords" CONTENT="lawsuit,lawsuits,briefs,judicial,legal resource,news,attorneys,court briefs,memos,law,laws,lawyer,attorney,legal,legal news,court,courts,legal research,law library,legal documents,counsel,counsel connect,american lawyer media,lawyer search,classified,classifieds,QRFP,Q.R.F.P.">
<META NAME="description" CONTENT="If you've had difficulty locating an attorney to handle your legal needs, Counsel Connect has the answer:  QRFP, a free attorney directory service for the business community. With QRFP (that's Quick Request for Proposals) Counsel Connect does the hard part: locating experienced lawyers in your geographical region who know how to handle your problem because they've done it a dozen, or a hundred, or a thousand times before. You send us a message describing your problem, and we forward it to qualified lawyers who want to bid for your business.">
</HEAD>
<BODY VLINK=FF0000 BGCOLOR=FFFFFF>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="http://www.counsel.com/cgi-bin/htimage/images/qrfp1.map"><IMG ISMAP BORDER=0 WIDTH=477 HEIGHT=72 SRC="/images/qrfp1.gif" ALT="QRFP - Quick Request for Proposals"></A></P>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="0" CELLSPACING="5">
<TR>

<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=CENTER>
<! Generated by place_ad, W3.COM, 1996><! Ad placement failed for '2702' (no available graphics. *BDEad*. jj)><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>

<TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=CENTER>
<! Generated by place_ad, W3.COM, 1996><! Ad placement failed for '4702' (no available graphics. *KILLINGad*. jj)><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>

<TD ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=CENTER>
<! Generated by place_ad, W3.COM, 1996><! Ad placement failed for '5702' (no available graphics. *HEINTZad*. jj)><BR CLEAR=ALL>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><B>If you're a businessperson or corporate counsel and have had difficulty locating an attorney to handle your legal needs, Counsel Connect has the answer:<P> QRFP, a free attorney directory service for the business community.</B></P>

<P>With QRFP (that's Quick Request for Proposals) <A HREF="/inside/about.html">Counsel Connect</A> does the hard part: locating experienced lawyers in your geographical region who know how to handle your problem because they've done it a dozen, or a hundred, or a thousand times before. You send us a message describing your problem, and we forward it to qualified lawyers who want to bid for your business.</P>

<P>We take steps to confirm that these lawyers have experience in the appropriate areas by checking the references they provide. As the largest online network for lawyers and part of American Lawyer Media (which publishes <I>The American Lawyer</I> magazine and manages Court TV), we have contacts at the most prestigious and experienced law firms around the world. Our QRFP panels are made up of the best qualified lawyers practicing in the U.S. and beyond. The good news is, this service is free -- it doesn't cost you anything to conduct a search for the right lawyer!</P>

<P>Here's how it works. You submit a short form by e-mail to Counsel Connect, describing your legal needs. Then we send it to lawyers who have tangible expertise in that area of the law in the geographic region you need. You get proposals back by private e-mail within hours or days, on the deadlines you specify. All panel members belong to Counsel Connect, the largest online network for attorneys.</P>

<P>If your question is not business related, please visit <A HREF="http://www.courttv.com/legalhelp/lawyer">Try Out Your Lawyer</A>, a consumer version of QRFP offered in partnership with the Court TV Law Center.</P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="qrfpmap.map"><IMG WIDTH=250 HEIGHT=40 ISMAP SRC="/images/qrfpmap.gif" BORDER=0></A></P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=-2><TT><A HREF="/qrfp/qrfpform.html">Submit Form</A> <B>&#183;</B>  <A HREF="/qrfp/quest.html">Questions?</A> <B>&#183;</B>  <A HREF="/inside/about.html">About Counsel Connect</A></FONT></P>

