<H2>The-Squib
</H2><HR>The SQUIB is Counsel Connect's weekly e-letter announcing hot, new legal happenings and offerings.  The Squib covers Counsel Connect, "the largest online service exclusively for lawyers," along with its website, Counsel Connect Web, as well as the Internet and the nonvirtual legal world .<P> The SQUIB reports on Counsel Connect's online seminars, workshops, interactive interviews with lawyers in the news, and other online happenings. With the Squib you'll find  out about newly minted legal discussion groups, hot docs behind the headlines, breaking legal news, businesses currently seeking counsel, and great new websites.<P> The Squib is for lawyers and other cybercitizens.<P> See you on The Squib.<P> Jesse Londin<P> Counsel Connect Senior law editor<P> <A HREF=mailto:buzz@counsel.com>buzz@counsel.com</A>  
