                <TR><TD WIDTH=200 ALIGN=right>
               
<PRE>


</PRE>
</TD>

                <TR><TD WIDTH=200 valign=top align=right>



                <HR SIZE=4><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR=red><I>

'I can only say that on the evidence then available, I would have concurred in charging even if the bond sale evidence were not available.'<!-- PULL QUOTE HERE -->
                </FONT><BR><FONT SIZE=+1 COLOR=black>

-- Ira Raphaelson<!-- QUOTE ATTRIBUTE HERE -->

        </I></FONT><br><HR SIZE=2></TD>


                <TR><TD WIDTH=200>
                <PRE>






</PRE></TD>

                <TR><TD WIDTH=200 valign=top align=right>
<HR SIZE=4><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR=red><I>

'It's one thing to say that Keating should be civilly liable to his investors for their losses. But wasn't it a stretch for the government to prosecute him under these circumstances?'<!-- PULL QUOTE HERE -->
                </FONT><BR><FONT SIZE=+1 COLOR=black>

-- Peter Scheer<!-- QUOTE ATTRIBUTE HERE -->

        </I></FONT><br><HR SIZE=2></TD>



                </TABLE>


        
        </BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE>
        </FONT>
        <P>
<! sidebar refers here>
<P>
