<DOCNO>WT07-B32-120</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000236-B002-36</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.counsel.com:80/features/keat3.html 199.29.97.41 19970108012158 text/html 9260
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 01:31:34 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 00:45:51 GMT
