<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Charles Keating: Scoundrel or Scapegoat? Take 3</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#ffffff LINK=#cd661d VLINK=#008b8b>


<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="http://www.counsel.com/images/lcc.gif">

<BLOCKQUOTE>

<BR><FONT COLOR=FF0000 SIZE=+3>COUNSEL CONNECT WEB</FONT><BR CLEAR=ALL>

</blockquote>

<CENTER>

<h2>Charles Keating:<BR>
Scoundrel or Scapegoat?</h2></CENTER>



        <TABLE WIDTH=650 cellspacing=20>



<TR><TD WIDTH=200></TD>


<TD WIDTH=450 ALIGN=right> 
<FONT SIZE=+2>Take 3</FONT></TD></TR>

                <TR>
                <TD WIDTH=200 ALIGN=right VALIGN=top>
                
                <P>Go to:<BR>
                <FONT SIZE=+2><A HREF=keat.html>Introduction</A></FONT><P>
                <FONT SIZE=+2><A HREF=keat1.html>Take 1</A></FONT><P>           
                <FONT SIZE=+2><A HREF=keat2.html>Take 2</A></FONT><P>           
                <FONT SIZE=+2><A HREF=keat3.html>Take 3</A></FONT>              

</TD>


                

<TD WIDTH=450 ROWSPAN=8 VALIGN=top>

<FONT Size=+1>



