<HtML>
<title>Counsel Connect Web - Caldera v. Microsoft</title>
<BODY bgcolor=ffffff text="000000" link="000080" vlink="ff0000">
<img width=100 height=92 align=left src="/images/spotlight/spt2.gif"> 

<P>Editor's Note: Caldera, Inc. brought an antitrust suit against
Microsoft, alleging that MS monopolizes the DOS market; practices
illegal tying; practices exclusive dealing; and tortiously interferes
with economic relations. Caldera bought a line of computers products
called DR DOS from the Novell Corporation, and alleges that MS practices
severely limit the product line's market share.</P>

<PRE>

</PRE>

