<h3>FDA
LACKS JURISDICTION OVER CIGARETTES</h3>
A.  Introduction..............I-1<P>
B.  FDA
Has No Jurisdiction Over Any<BR>
Currently Marketed Brand of Cigarettes......I-3<P>
1. 
Congress Has Withheld From FDA Any<BR>
Authority To Regulate
Cigarettes........I-5<P>
2.  Congress Responded to the 1964<BR>
Surgeon General's
Report by Creating<BR>
a Comprehensive Program for Cigarette<BR>
Regulation, Which
Excludes Any Role for<BR>
FDA ................I-7<P>
