Congress<BR>
Has Continued To Deny FDA<BR>
Jurisdiction Over Cigarettes;<BR>
and FDA Has --
Until August, 1995 --<BR>
Accepted and Adhered to that Decision.......I-12<P>
4.  The
Courts Have Consistently<BR>
Recognized That FDA Has No<BR>
Jurisdiction Over
Cigarettes........I-19<P>
5.  By Asserting Jurisdiction over<BR>
Cigarettes, FDA Has
Defied Congress.....I-29<P>
