<H3> A PRODUCT IS A DRUG OR DEVICE UNDER THE
FEDERAL<BR>
FOOD, DRUG, AND COSMETIC ACT BASED ON CLAIMS<BR>
MADE BY THE MANUFACTURER IN
MARKETING THE PRODUCT</H3>

A.  Claims That a Product Affects the<BR>
Structure or
Function of the Body<BR>
Must Address Significant Effects<BR>
for Medical
Purposes............   II-2<P>
