II-110<P>
9. Thyroid Products.......... II-111<P>
c.  A Manufacturer's Objective
Intent<BR>
 Cannot Be Demonstrated Through<BR>
Physician Use of a Product.......
II-111<P>
1. Cameron Spitler Case.......... II-111<P>
