                </TD>
        </TR>
</TABLE><P>

<font color="ff1111" font size=5><center>Legal Information That Saves You Time</CENTER></FONT><P>

<font color="0000000" font size=3><BR>Counsel Connect contains some of the most valuable legal information anywhere -- and our easy search system makes it easy to find what you need without wasting lots of time.  Researching an issue that you're sure someone else has analyzed?  You can run a quick search to see if one of the thousands of memos or briefs in our Library is on point.  Counsel Connect's Library also contains case summaries, court opinions and other materials covering a broad range of topics.

<P>Looking for published information about a client or company?  Counsel Connect's News area allows you to search dozens of different news sources and locate articles and stories instantly.  You can even store your searches and re-run them at a later date to save time.  And you can print anything you find, save it to a disk, or send it via Counsel Connect's e-mail system to a friend or colleague -- all at no extra charge.</FONT></P>
