Like the live, in-person seminars you've attended,  Counsel Connect's online
seminars 
feature top-notch panels and give attendees  collections of current and
relevant reference documents.  The big difference: Counsel Connect Seminars are
interactive. 
Panelists discuss the issues and attendees  ask questions at any time.
 Guaranteed, no one  drones on for 45 minutes as you fight to stay awake! 
</P><P>
Seminar attendees participate by reading faculty comments and posing their own
direct questions, contributing their expertise to the seminar and raising the
issues they'd like to see addressed. Since 1995 we've produced more than <a

href="/inside/seminars/pastsems.html">120 online 
seminars</a> with known specialists from around the world. 
If you're a lawyer, we hope you'll join us for some of our upcoming events. 
