<font color="ff1111" font size=5><center>The Smart Law Library</CENTER></FONT><P>

<font color="0000000" font size=3><BR>Counsel Connect's library contains more than 30,000 legal memos, briefs, case summaries, court opinions and other materials covering a broad range of topics under both federal and state law.  From advertising law to medical malpractice to securities law, the memos on Counsel Connect -- many authored by the top firms in the U.S. -- can cut your research time by getting you answers quickly.
<P>To provide you with cutting-edge legal analysis at your desk, our library also contains briefs and pleadings selected by our staff of legal editors from the most significant and noteworthy cases in the courts todays.<P>Counsel Connect's library has an intuitive search system that you'll find easy to use -- you can even store your searches and re-run them at a later date to save time.  You can print what you find, save it to a disk or send it via Counsel Connect's e-mail system to a friend or colleague -- all at no extra charge.</FONT></P>
<P>
