<HEAD>

<TITLE>About Counsel Connect</TITLE>
        <META>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" VLINK="000000" LINK="000000">

<TABLE><TABLE WIDTH="100%" BORDER=0><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER WITDTH="20%"><IMG SRC="images/LOGO.GIF"></TD>
                
                <TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="60%">
                        <IMG SRC="images/JOINHEAD.GIF">
                </TD>

                <TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="20%">
                        <A HREF="join.html"><IMG SRC="images/JOINLOOP.GIF" BORDER=0></A>
                </TD>
        </TR>
</TABLE><P>


<FONT color="000000" font size=6><center>About Counsel Connect</CENTER></B> </font><BR>



Founded in 1993 as a division of American Lawyer Media, Counsel Connect is the largest subscriber online service for lawyers, with a current membership of more than 43,000 legal professionals that gain access to Counsel Connect via our proprietary software.  <P>Members benefit from 200 expert-led legal discussion groups organized by practice area, online seminars on a wide variety of topics covering substantive law and areas of interest to lawyers, and an online library with more than 30,000 briefs, legal memos and other materials updated daily by Counsel Connect's staff of editors.  <P>Members also get access, at no extra charge, to legal news and Counsel Connect's "Private" feature, which allows our members to create online areas where they can store documents and hold private discussions.<P>
<TABLE WIDTH="100%">
        <TR>
                <TD ALIGN=RIGHT>
                        <B><font color="ff1111" font size=3><A HREF="inside.html"><IMG SRC="images/RETURN.GIF" BORDER=0 ALIGN=RIGHT></TD>
                <TD ALIGN=CENTER>
                        <A HREF="join.html"><IMG SRC="images/JOIN2.GIF" BORDER=0></A>
                </TD>
        </TR>
