<HTML>



<HEAD>



<TITLE>Why Lawyers Only?</TITLE>

        <META>

</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" VLINK="000000" LINK="000000"><A NAME="TOP"><TABLE><TABLE WIDTH="100%" BORDER=0><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER WITDTH="20%"><IMG SRC="images/LOGO.GIF"></TD>

                

                <TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="60%">

                        <IMG SRC="images/JOINHEAD.GIF">

                </TD>



                <TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="20%">

                        <A HREF="join.html"><IMG SRC="images/JOINLOOP.GIF" BORDER=0></A>

                </TD>

        </TR>

</TABLE><P>



<font color="000000" font size=5><center>Why Lawyers Only?</CENTER></FONT><P>



<BLOCKQUOTE>

Counsel Connect restricts membership to practicing lawyers and their professional staff, working under the supervision of a lawyer-member, so that all members are assured that discussion participants have a basic level of expertise and have knowingly agreed to the rules that govern the discussions.<P>

This allows Counsel Connect to create a focused and like-minded community and provide a high level of discussion already filtered of the usual Internet noise.<P>

<TABLE WIDTH="100%">

        <TR>

                <TD ALIGN=LEFT>

                        <B><font color="ff1111" font size=3><A HREF="inside.html"><IMG SRC="images/RETURN.GIF" BORDER=0></A></B> </font>

                </TD>

                <TD ALIGN=CENTER>

                        <A HREF="join.html"><IMG SRC="images/JOIN2.GIF" BORDER=0></A>

                </TD>

        </TR>

</TABLE>

