<A NAME="PRICE">

<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Counsel Connect Subscription Fees</TITLE>
        <META>
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff" VLINK="000000" LINK="000000"><A NAME="TOP"><TABLE><TABLE WIDTH="100%" BORDER=0><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER WITDTH="20%"><IMG SRC="images/LOGO.GIF"></TD>
                
                <TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="60%">
                        <IMG SRC="images/JOINHEAD.GIF">
                </TD>

                <TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="20%">
                        <A HREF="join.html"><IMG SRC="images/JOINLOOP.GIF" BORDER=0></A>
                </TD>
        </TR>
</TABLE><P>

<B><font color="ff1111" font size=4><CENTER>CURRENT PRICING</CENTER></B></font>


<!SPELLCHECK11/5!>
                <P><B>Individual Pricing.</B> You can choose from one of three price plans designed to suit the needs and budget of every lawyer:</P>

        <UL>
                <P><B><LI>One-Year Membership:</B> You pay one annual payment of $119.40 (that's only
$9.95 per month).
                <B><LI>Six-Month Membership:</B> You pay $69 (that's only $11.50 per month).
                <B><LI>Monthly Membership:</B> You pay $12.50 per month.</P>
        </UL>

<P>All three price plans include unlimited usage when you use our Windows software to connect to Counsel
Connect through your own Internet Service Provider (i.e. MCI, Netcom, etc). If you don't have an Internet account or are using a Macintosh or DOS system, you can use Counsel Connect's regular dialup network for just $3 per hour.
</P>

Your membership fees include a one-year (four issue) $25.00 subscription to <FONT SIZE=2><B>AMLAW TECH: THE AMERICAN LAWYER'S TECHNOLOGY MAGAZINE</B></FONT>.

<P><B>Group pricing plans</B> are available; please call 800-569-4086 for more details.</P>

                </TD>
</TR>
