<FONT SIZE=2><TT><A HREF="about.html">ABOUT COUNSEL CONNECT</a> <B>…</B> <A HREF="attonly.html">WHY LAWYERS ONLY</A> <B>…</B> <A HREF="price.html">SUBSCRIPTION FEES</a> <B>…</B> <A HREF="mailto:joining@counsel.com">SEND US E-MAIL</a></font></P>



<FONT SIZE=1 FONT COLOR="FFFFFF">Counsel Connect is the largest online communications network exclusively for lawyers, serving over 30,000 law professionals nationwide. Members take advantage of a variety of discussions on substantive law topics, posted requests for proposals, online legal seminars and private conferencing options, in addition to such resources as legal news and a 30,000-volume law library. Unlike traditional legal Web services, Counsel Connect is exclusive to law professionals.</FONT>



