<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF=http://www.ita.doc.gov/import_admin/records>Import Administration</A></FONT>



<BR>

<UL>

Meet the office in the Department of Commerce responsible for "safeguarding American industries and jobs against unfair trade practices." Visit Import Administration for text of antidumping and countervailing duty notices posted in the Federal Register. Catch highlights of Import Administration ongoing programs, and check currency exchange rates.

</UL>







<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF=http://www.xballot.org>xballot: Absentee Ballot Request Server</A></FONT>



<BR>

<UL>

Election Day approaches. Every netizen may vote by snail mail with an absentee ballot. Come to xballot to fill out a form for requesting a mail-in ballot from local election offices in any state. The site also presents absentee ballot request deadlines and other important state election rules. Don't forget to vote.

</UL>



<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF=http://njlawnet.com/ipindex/ipnav.html>Intellectual Property Index</A></FONT>



<BR>

<UL>

For IP lawyers everywhere, this searchable directory from New Jersey Law Network and W3 Lawyer collects links to a good variety of legal resources including articles, organizations, updates, government offices and more. Featuring the following categories: general IP resources, computer law, copyright, multimedia, trademark, patent and cyberspace law.

</UL>





<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF=http://www.arthurandersen.com/bus_info/industry/resg>Arthur Andersen Real Estate Services Group</A></FONT>



<BR>

