</UL>







<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF=http://www.access.gpo.gov/osc>U.S. Office of Special Counsel</A></FONT>

<UL>

<BR>What federal arm investigates reprisals against whistleblowers and partisan political activity by government employees?  Meet the OSC, the independent agency responsible for investigating prohibited personnel practices and Hatch Act violations. Learn about the office's policies and procedures.  Access the OSC's hotline for whistleblowers.

</UL>



<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF=http://38.15.20.146/2cents/Twocent2.htm>Our Two Cents - A Virtual Debtor-Creditor Newsletter</A></FONT>

