<B>

<a href="http://www.epa.gov/docs/acidrain/">Acid Rain Program</a></B>

<ul>



Title IV of the Clean Air Act mandates reductions in sulfer dioxide and nitrogen oxides emmissions

from burning fossil fuel -- the primary causes of acid rain.  Put on your galashes and splash over

to the EPA's Acid Rain Division for background on the program and the effects of acid rain and air

pollutiion. Featuring tracking system summaries, allowance and emmissions data, Policy Manual

Updates, regulations and more.





</ul>





