<P>





<a href="http://cisgw3.law.pace.edu/"><B>Institute of International Commercial Law - CISG

Database</B></a>

<ul>

The United Nations Convention of the International Sale of Goods (CISG),

adopted in 1980, regulates the formation of international sales

contracts and the rights and remedies of parties to those contracts. 

Pace University's Institute has compiled a comprehensive database of

CISG materials, including text of the treaty, background, cases,

articles and other noteworthy resources.

</UL>

</P>

