<ul>



Everyone knows about the branch of the Department of Health & Human

Services responsible for monitoring one trillion dollars worth of food,

medicine and other products per year. Visit the FDA's webspace to inspect

FDA's budget, its mission and vision statements, history and organization,

and reports and information about  human and animal drugs, biologics,

cosmetics, medical devices and more.  And don't forget to read the label.

</ul>



