articles on biotech patents, "inevitable disclosure," patent protection

legislation, "culture vultures" and advice to start-up companies. Dive into

past issues of Intellectual Property.  And follow pointers to Cal Law,

Briefing Papers and intellectual property law links.

</ul>





</P>

