<b>

<a href="http://www.rand.org:80/centers/icj/">The Institute for Civil Justice (ICJ)</a>

</b><ul>



Do plaintiffs win more in medical malpractice cases or contract actions? 

Did an 1980s "explosion" in mass tort litigation frighten manufacturers

and insurers from risky markets? Rand's Institute reports on trends in

civil justice.  Read summaries of recent studies and search abstracts of

Rand publications.

</ul>





