<P><FONT SIZE="+2" color="000000"><LI><TT><B>Week of July 8:</B></TT></font> </P>



<P>

<B>

<a href="http://www.law.georgetown.edu/lc/internic/recent/rec1.html">Domain Names Disputes</a></B>

<ul>



Candyland, Roadrunner, MTV, Dole96: From domain name "grabbing" to innocent

registration of someone else's name or slogan, how does trademark law

protect those suffering from an identity crisis in cyberspace?  Here's a

excellent roundup of domain name cases and controversies involving

InterNIC, the NSI and the online community.





</ul>

