technology.  What's the latest from the White House? Stop by this electronic

briefing room for the executive scoop.  Read daily and weekly press releases and

briefings and recent presidential speeches.  Browse or search the 1995 and 1996

budgets.  And while you're here, subscribe to the White House's daily

publications e-mail service.

</ul>



</p><P>



<B> <a href="http://www.courttv.com/seminars/violence/">Workplace Violence - Seminar</a></B><ul>

Whether it's harassment, a domestic  dispute which spills over to the 

workplace, or an employee who has interpersonal problems, workplace violence

is a problem for employers and employees alike. This seminar, taking place on Counsel Connect

and accessible on the Court TV Law Center, explores the limits of the employer's obligations under

the common law, regulations, and statutes.

</ul>

