who have applied within the last three months need not re-apply.
In addition, the Office of International Affairs has openings for
attorneys with experience relating to international issues,
including regulatory initiatives, trade negotiations, and
technical assistance.  Persons interested in this position must
call the SEC Job Hotline at (202) 942-4150 and request a copy of
the applicable vacancy announcement.  Salary $44,458 - $82,483.
We are an EEO Employer.<P>

