http://www.counsel.com:80/counselquote/canvas.html 199.29.97.41 19970108013429 text/html 3360
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 01:44:07 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 14:26:19 GMT
