<html><TITLE>QRFP Service - online proposal request form</TITLE><body
vlink=ff0000 bgcolor=ffffff><P align=center><a href="http://www.counsel.com/cgi-bin/htimage/images/qrfp1.map"><img ISMAP border=0  width=477 height=72 src=/images/qrfp1.gif alt="QRFP -
 Quick Request for Proposals"></a></P><P>



<P>
<blockquote>
<H3>Submission Form</H3>
Here are some guidelines for submitting QRFPs to our standing panels.
They are
intentionally general, because we feel the QRFP should be less
bureaucratic and
formulaic than a standard-issue RFP.

<P>

However, this is just a template -- you should feel free to ask
additional
questions dictated by the nature of the matter you need handled.
Remember: You
can affect the quantity and quality of responses by making your
request as
detailed as you wish.



<P>

PLEASE NOTE:<P>

<LI>Any information provided on this submission is not in any way
confidential.
<P>
<LI>This submission does not in any way create an attorney-client
relationship with either Counsel Connect or any lawyer that responds.
<P>
<LI>By submitting the information and agreeing to use this QRFP service,
you agree that Counsel Connect assumes no liability or responsibility
with respect to the information provided or any subsequent action
taken by you or any lawyer that you may select.

<blockquote><P>
<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="http://www.counsel.com/cgi-bin/form-mail">
<input type=hidden NAME="TO" VALUE="tdrucker@counsel.com"><Input
type=hidden NAME="SUBJECT" VALUE="QRFP_FORM_REPLY">


<B>REQUIRED INFORMATION:</B><br>

<inPUT SIZE=30 NAME="NAME"> First and last name<BR>



<inPUT SIZE=30 NAME="TITLE"> Title<BR>

            

<inPUT SIZE=30 NAME="FIRM"> Firm or company<BR>

<inPUT SIZE=30 NAME="CITY/STATE"> City and State<BR>

        

<inPUT SIZE=30 NAME="FROM"> E-mail address<br>



<inPUT SIZE=30 NAME="PHONE"> Phone number<P>

<I>Note: You must fill in your INTERNET e-mail address to receive a
response.</I><P>

 How did you hear about Q.R.F.P.? (If you ran a search, saw a link from another site, or saw an ad, please be specific)<BR>
<inPUT SIZE=46 NAME="I heard about QRFP from"><P>

<B>DESCRIBE YOUR LEGAL PROBLEM:</B>

<br><TEXTAREA NAME="PROBLEM_DESCRIPTION" rows="8"
cols="43"></textarea>

<P>

<B>WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW ABOUT THE LAWYERS?</B> Examples:
educational
background; experience in related legal matters; billing rates;
alternative
billing schedules; who would be doing the actual work; how they bill
for extras
like phone calls, research and photocopies.

 <TEXTAREA NAME= "TERMS_OF_PROPOSED_MATTER" rows="8"
cols="43"></textarea>

<P>

<B>WHAT DO THE LAWYERS NEED TO <br> KNOW ABOUT YOU AND YOUR
BUSINESS?</B
Examples: Are you a partnership, corporation or sole proprietor? How
many employees do you
have? Where are your operations based?<br>

 <TEXTAREA NAME=  "ABOUT_FIRM" rows="8" cols="43"></textarea><P>

<P>

<B>DO YOU WANT REFERENCES FROM OTHER CLIENTS?</B><P><UL>

<input type=radio name="SEND_REFERENCES" VALUE="yes">Yes 

<input type=radio name="SEND_REFERENCES" VALUE="no">No</ul>





<b>Final proposals are due: <inPUT SIZE=10
NAME="PRPOSALS_DUE:"></b><P>

Note: As a courtesy to the lawyers who will be responding to your
request,
please wait until this deadline passes before choosing someone to
handle your
legal matter.<P>


<b><font size=4>I</font> heard of QRFP from:</b> 
<select name="Heard_About">
<option> (select below)
<option>Counsel Connect Web
<option>a friend/associate
<option>an Internet Search
<option>a Big Yellow ad
<option>a Yahoo! ad
<option>other</select>


<P><BR><BR>
<center>

<INPUT TYPE="submit" value="Send this QRFP"></form>
<form action="http://www.counsel.com/">
<INPUT TYPE="submit" value="Cancel this QRFP"></form>
</center>

</form><P>



</body></html>




</DOC>
